<D>__{my mom's been pretty sad the past few months. she deserves to be happy. my dad obviously is... wherever he is.}
<C>__{mike}
<D>__{maybe he's not? maybe he wishes he could be here right now with you but there's a real good reason he can't be.}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{no, my dad's not a family guy. this is dumb but i used to tell him i}
<A>__{was on the basketball team because i knew he'd never make it to a game.}
<C>__{mike}
<D>__{then why would you tell him that?}
